fields.name: Aero Champion Ladies Shoes
fields.description:
Aero Champion Ladies Bowls Shoes, made of extra soft artificial leather, are designed to provide outstanding comfort.

Features:

* Strong heel counter.
* Leather covered EVA inner sole and leather lined inner provide coolness.

fields.name: Aero Flex Mens Shoes
fields.description:
Aero Flex Mens Bowls Shoes are a quality Bowling shoe.

Features:

* Flexing front for ease in bending.
* Arch support.
* Heel area with a measured counter to provide perfect lateral support for correct gait.
* EVA inner sole for odour reduction and comfort.
* Outer material has been updated so that it may be wiped down if required.

fields.name: Aero Nirvana Ladies Shoes
fields.description: Aero Nirvana Ladies Bowls Shoes are comfortable shoes and made to suit a wide to narrow foot.

fields.name: Aero Nirvana Mens Shoes
fields.description: Aero Nirvana Mens Bowls Shoes are comfortable shoes and made to suit the widest to the narrowest foot.

fields.name: Crown Velcro Mens Shoes
fields.description: The Crown Velcro Fastening Mens Bowls shoes represent great value for money. They have a leather upper with nicely padded insoles that provide a good degree of 'bounce'. The soles are non slip too.

fields.name: Drakes Pride Astro Unisex Shoes
fields.description:
The Astro Drakes Pride Bowls Shoes are the ultimate in terms of their design, comfort, style and technology. They feature a soft EVA midsole which allows for light, flexible and resilient cushioning, and the hard wearing micro grip rubber outer single piece sole surface makes this shoe truly heel-less and Bowling Green friendly.

Features:
*Soft and luxurious EVA innersole
*Featherweight, form-fitting, virtually seamless microfibre flyknit upper providing the ultimate in comfort, flexibility and breathability.

fields.name: Drakes Pride Cosmic-2 Ladies Shoes
fields.description:
Drakes Pride Cosmic 2 Ladies Bowls Shoes is an upgraded version of a very popular trainer style that has been around for many years. 

Features:
* Drakes Pride's moulded sole, and the hi-tech breathable material from which the shoe is manufactured 
   makes this an incredibly lightweight and comfortable Bowling shoe. 
* They are regular fitting. 
* The micro-grip rubber sole base also helps to prevent slipping.

fields.name: Hensilite HL72 Ladies Shoes
fields.description:
The Ladies HL72 Bowls Shoes are like no other Bowls shoes you've ever seen. They are quite simply unique. Fashionable and look stunning with grey or black trousers. 

Features:
* Lightweight outer sole too making the whole shoe extremely comfortable to wear. 
* A woven upper, complete with a choice of attractive alternative laces included with each pair.  
* To assist with sizing each shoe has a second, removable, insole.

fields.name: Hensilite HL74
fields.description:
The Henselite Ladies HL74 Sports Bowls Shoes with IMPACT X Technology has a high quality PU upper that is part breathable. 

Features:
* It has a lightweight outer sole
* Includes an inner sole with an additional absorption layer engineered to provide additional comfort
* IMPACT X Technology 
* Memory foam inner sole unit also adds an extra level of comfort.
* Each pair comes with a complementing colour second lace option.

fields.name: Hensilite HL74 Mens Shoes
fields.description:
The Henselite HM74 Mens Sport Bowls Shoes with IMPACT X Technology has a high quality PU upper that is part breathable. I

Features:
* Lightweight outer sole 
* Inner sole with an additional absorption layer engineered to provide additional comfort
* IMPACT X Technology
* Memory foam inner sole unit also adds an extra level of comfort.
* Each pair comes with white laces and a complimenting coloured second lace option and complimentary 
   pair of Henselite socks.

fields.name: Taylor Apollo Shoes
fields.description:
Taylor Apollo Mens Bowls Shoes are a full leather upper trainer style Bowls shoe.  For those who like the trainer style but prefer something without colour, then this is perfect.

Features:
* The leather makes them very comfortable 
* Sole has been improved to provide exceptional grip

fields.name: Drakes Pride Drakelock Steel Measure
fields.description:
The Drakes Pride Drakelock 10ft Steel Bowls measure with calipers for those really tight measures. 

NB// Avaliable colours shown on image

fields.name: Drakes Pride Marker Pouch
fields.description:
The Drakes Pride Lawn Bowls Marker Pouch is an ideal leather pouch to hold your spray chalk and measure. It has a clip to attach to the waistband of both trousers or skirts.

NB// Please note that the accessories shown in the image are there for illustrative purposes only. Both can be bought separately from within our Bowls Supplies section if the combination appeals. 
A RINKLOCK MEASURE WILL NOT FIT INSIDE THIS POUCH!.

fields.name: Drakes Pride Measuring Calipers
fields.description: The Drakes Pride 6" Bowls Measuring Calipers are a must for Umpires or who 'Marks' regularly.

fields.name: Drakes Pride Fibre Bowls Measuring Tape
fields.description:
The Drakes Pride 30m. (100') Fibre Bowls Measuring Tape is a recommeded purchase for umpires and  whole-club use. 

NB// This particular tape is included in the Lawn Green Official Umpires' Bowls Kit found at "Accessories/Club Equipment"

fields.name: Drakes Pride Rinklock Measure
fields.description:
The Drakes Pride Rinklock 11ft. String Bowls Measure is an 11 Foot String Bowls Measure that comes complete with Calipers and a Belt Clip.

NB// Rinklock measure will not fit inside the Drakes Pride Bowls Marker Pouch.

fields.name: Drakes Pride Anti-slip Rubber Wedges
fields.description:
Anti-slip rubber Bowls wedges,  used to prevent angled bowls from falling over during a measure.
Sold as a set of 4.

Carefully place wedges under a bowl before the measure, may prevent a lot of grief and a long, lonely walk home!

fields.name: Drakes Pride Scorecard Holder
fields.description:
The Drakes Pride Rigid Bowls Scorecard Holder is one of our best sellers.
Scorecard is held by a spring clip and there's a pen holder inside.

fields.name: Drakes Pride Spray Chalk 3-Pack
fields.description:
Pack of 3 Drakes Pride Spray Chalk, bargain at just £10 (£4 individually).

Features:
* Used by Umpires and Bowlers Worldwide 
* Spray on, 
* Water based 
* Easy to wipe off 
* Ozone friendly

NB// to make these sprays work the canister must be held upside down - as you would when marking a bowl.

fields.name: Drakes Pride Spray Chalk
fields.description:
Individual Drakes Pride Spray Chalk.

Features:
* Used by Umpires and Bowlers Worldwide 
* Spray on, 
* Water based 
* Easy to wipe off 
* Ozone friendly

NB// Image for visual purposes, this is a purchase for one canister of chalk spray. To make spray work the canister must be held upside down - as you would when marking a bowl

fields.name: Drakes Pride Spray Chalk Boxes
fields.description:
Box of 20 Drakes Pride Spray Chalk. Ideal for club stock.

Features:
* Used by Umpires and Bowlers Worldwide 
* Spray on, 
* Water based 
* Easy to wipe off 
* Ozone friendly

NB// to make these sprays work the canister must be held upside down - as you would when marking a bowl.

fields.name: Drakes Pride String Measure
fields.description: The Drakes Pride String Measure (15ft) has adjustable pegs on a flexible string making it ideal for ditch measuring or long measures (over 11ft).

fields.name: Drakes Pride Supalock Gold Measure
fields.description:
The Drakes Pride Supalock Gold Measure is a 9ft. string bowls measure with a belt clip and set of calipers folded into the base.

NB// Colour choices as per image shown.

fields.name: Hensilite Clubhawk Gold Measure
fields.description:
The Henselite Clubhawk Gold Measure is a very popular string bowls measure and has been improved with ABS (Advanced Braking System), a device that improves measuring accuracy.

The measure extends up to 9ft and also include fixed calipers in the base and belt clip.

fields.name: Drakes Pride Crack-a-Jack Polish
fields.description: Drakes Pride Crack-a-Jack Polish remains a popular, traditional bowls polish, that can improve grip in all-weather conditions and be used to give your bowls that extra shine!

fields.name: Drakes Pride Get-A-Grip Cloth
fields.description:
If your hand keeps slipping while bowling then the Drakes Pride Get-A-Grip is for you. It's a tacky cloth for your fingers - not for use on the bowl itself though.

How To Use:
* Cut a small piece off and place it inside something similar to a money bag (the sort used in banks).
* Reseal the main Get-A-Grip bag and save it. 
* When bowling, just slip your fingers into the money bag in your pocket, and touch the cloth to transfer the 
   grip to your fingers.

Features:
* Use as often as you like.
* Safe for hands and gloves.
* Prevents over-gripping.
* Will not stain.
* Non toxic.
* Re-sealable bag.

fields.name: Drakes Pride Feeler Guage Set
fields.description:
The Drakes Pride Feeler Guage Set is ideal for those close shots. No Umpire should be without them. 

NB// The guage is included in the Official Umpires' Kit located at Accessories/Club Equipment.

fields.name: Drakes Pride Gadd Measure
fields.description:
The Drakes Pride Gadd Measure is a durable 30 metre metal bowls tape, typically used to measure Jack length. It's a valuable piece of kit for Umpires in particular, and EVERY club should have one.

WARNING! - This item is has a button to retract the tape, it is advised to apply enough pressure to collect tape, but not so much that it might nip your fingers!

NB// This is the only retail image Drakes Pride have provided and it shows the measure has a brake built in, however this is not the case for the sale item.

fields.name: Drakes Pride Microfibre Towel
fields.description:
The Drakes Pride Microfibre Towel is a soft microfibre towel. Dimesions measure: 55cms x 25cms. 
Unlike the traditional bowls towel the microfibre doesn't get saturated and thus remains effective throughout a match.

fields.name: Drakes Pride Bowl Sheen
fields.description: The Drakes Pride Bowl Sheen polish is a specially formulated compound for removing small scratches from composition Bowls.

fields.name: Hensilite Bulldog Grip
fields.description:
Henselite Bulldog Grip wax blocks are a tried and tested product that provides an all purpose sports grip ideal for golf, tennis, squash and bowls. 

Simple but effective. 

It's easy to use; simply place a piece of the Bulldog Grip in your hands, squash it, and soften the block. This applies the wax in a thin film to your hand that acts as a superb gripping agent.

fields.name: Hensilite Grippo Screwcap Jar
fields.description:
The Henselite Grippo in a Screwtop Jar is a bowls polish and grip that has stood the test of time. It's a polish with that extra bit of "tackiness" than its namesake in the tube.

The original formula remains unchanged for over 50 years and is as popular today as ever.

fields.name: Hensilite Grippo Tube
fields.description:
Henselite Grippo Tube - the biggest selling bowls polish in the world. 

Assists with grip and easy to apply from the convenient screw cap (with piercer) tube. 

The formula remains unchanged for over 50 years: well why change it when it's as reliable and successful as this?

fields.name: Henselite Microfibre Quick Dry Cloth
fields.description:
The Henselite Microfibre Quick Dry Cloth is very effective in wet conditions. 

The fabric is water repellent and gives the perfect grip so you can deliver the perfect bowl ........ Or at least it will improve your chances or doing so!

fields.name: Hensilite Wilgrip Tube
fields.description:
Henselite Wilgrip is a concentrated gripping agent that's extremely effective in wet conditions. 
Use a tiny amount on the fingers and see just how good it is!

NB// Not recommended as a bowls polish.

fields.name: Taylor Grip-It Cloth
fields.description:
Taylor Bowls Grip-It is a cloth that when touched transfers a tacky grip to your fingers. It's really good stuff, no mess and it's very strong. Excellent in wet conditions.

How To Use:
* Cut a small piece off and place it inside something (similar to a money bag used in banks). 
* Reseal the main Grip-It Cloth bag and save it. 
* When bowling, slip your fingers into in your pocket, and touch the cloth and transfer the grip.

fields.name: Drakes Pride Outdoor Jack
fields.description: This Drakes Pride Outdoor Lawn/Flat Green Jack is a Standard 10oz. Jack specifically designed for the Lawn/Flat Green Outdoor game.

fields.name: Drakes Pride Bowls Gatherer
fields.description:
Drakes Pride Bowls Gatherer - take the stress out of collecting all those bowls each end with this Bowls Gatherer.

Made from coated tubular steel and wide easy move wheels. Easy self assembly.

Size of the collection area: Width - 100cm (39"), Depth - 50cm (19.5").

fields.name: Drakes Pride Ditch Markers
fields.description:
The Drakes Pride Ditch Markers are made of metal and, as implied, they're for marking where the bowl or Jack is positioned once in the ditch. 

They're a must for every Bowls Club - Indoors or Outdoors.

fields.name: Drakes Pride Horizontal Scoreboard
fields.description:
The Drakes Pride Horizontal Scoreboard

Features: 
* Solid steel tubular construction with aluminium.
* Scoreboard numbers supplied - Scores from 0 to 49. 
* Complete with ground spikes and feet.
* Score is visible from both sides - e.g.14 on playing side and 10+4 spectator side.

fields.name: Drakes Pride Vertical Scoreboard
fields.description:
The Drakes Pride Vertical Scoreboard

Features: 
* Solid steel tubular construction with aluminium.
* Scoreboard numbers supplied - Scores from 0 to 49. 
* Complete with ground spikes and feet.
* Score is visible from both sides - e.g.14 on playing side and 10+4 spectator side.

fields.name: Drakes Pride Umpire Kit
fields.description:
The Drakes Pride Umpires Kit is the Official Bowls Umpires' Kit as used at the Commonwealth Games and also used at all the major World Bowls Tour Events.

The Bowls Umpires' Kit consists of: 
Feeler Gauge, Callipers, Set Square, Score Lollipops, Magnifying Glass, Chalk Spray, Wedges, Supalock measure, Rinklock Measure, 30m fibre tape, Kneeling Pad, Bowls towel, Toucher Gauge.

fields.name: Hensilite Delivery Mats
fields.description:
Henselite Bowls Delivery Mats are regulation Bowls Delivery Mats. 
Slip resistant these mats are made of hard wearing rubber with a moulded grip for use in Flat Green

fields.name: Taylor Delivery Mats
fields.description:
Taylor Bowls Delivery Mats. 
World Bowls Board regulation rubber Lawn Bowls delivery mats.

fields.name: Taylor Outdoor Jack
fields.description:
The Taylor Outdoor Jack weighs a standard 10oz.
Specifically design for the Outdoor game.

fields.name: Aero Ladies Tartan Shirt
fields.description:
The Aero Tartan Ladies Shirt has an attractive modern design. 

This quality easy care lightweight and breathable Polo shirt will suit all generations of Bowlers.

fields.name: Aero Mens Tartan Shirt
fields.description: The Aero Tartan Mens Shirt has an attractive modern design that’s new to the Bowling market. This quality easy care lightweight and breathable Polo shirt will suit all generations of Bowlers.

fields.name: Drakes Pride Amelia Blouse
fields.description:
The Drakes Pride Amelia Ladies Blouse with its patterned black on white creates a truly unique and stylish shirt with a great feel. The material is super soft to handle and has a fluid drape.

The Sportec material from which this garment is made was developed using an innovative moisture management treatment. This ensures moisture is drawn away from the body for rapid evaporation keeping the body dry.

Features:
* 100% Sportec material.
* Stylish silver and black pattern.
* Moisture wicking and anti-bacterial.
* ¼ Chrome Zip.
* Leisure fit.

fields.name: Drakes Pride Avery Shirt
fields.description:
The Drakes Pride Avery Mens Bowls Shirt is a super soft, premium quality garment that offers real comfort when Bowling.

The 100% Sportec Pique material from which the Avery is made was developed using an innovative moisture management treatment. This ensures moisture is drawn away from the body keeping you nice and dry.

Features:
* 100% Sportec Pique material.
* Knitted collar and cuff with Jacquard detail in the collar. 
* Leisure fit.
* Three button placket.
* 150 GSM/UPF Rating - very good.

fields.name: Drakes Pride Bella Ladies Shirt
fields.description:
The Drakes Pride Bella Ladies Bowls Blouse not only looks good, it's truly comfortable as well. The material is super soft to handle and has a fluid drape.

The Sportec material from which this garment is made was developed using an innovative moisture management treatment. This ensures moisture is drawn away from the body for rapid evaporation keeping the body dry.

Features:

* 100% Sportec material.
* Stylish silver and black pattern on the side panels.
* Moisture wicking and anti-bacterial.
* 3 button placket.
* Leisure fit.

fields.name: Drakes Pride Dallas Shirt
fields.description:
The Drakes Pride Dallas Mens Shirt is a premium quality shirt that is extremely durable and one that will stand the test of time for the most active of Bowlers. It’s a classic shirt with the look and feel of a quality shirt, but at a very affordable price.

Features:
* 65% Polyester 35% Pique.
* Knitted collar and cuff with contrast edging.
* Contrast herringbone tape in back neck and side seam splits.
* Modern fit.
* Three button placket.
* 190-200 GSM/UPF Rating - very good.

fields.name: Drakes Pride Eva Bodywarmer
fields.description:
The Drakes Pride Eva Bodywarmer with Thermo-tec is not too bulky and is ideal as an extra layer. 

The diamond stitched patterned panels of lightweight quilted padding and internal storm flap give extra warmth and comfort.

The two zipped pockets are also a useful feature for hand warming or storage of your bowling accessories.

fields.name: Drakes Pride Ida Top
fields.description:
The Drakes Pride Ida Top is a long sleeved Bowls top. 
With its 94% Polyester and 6% Spandex material it's slightly thicker than the usual Bowls tops and that makes it extra warm - great for use as a single layer or as a base layer under other garments.

The elasticity of the garment makes it very comfortable to wear.
Finished with embroidered logo, sliver/white pattern piping and a ¼ zip neck opening for a stylish look.

fields.name: Drakes Pride Megan Blouse
fields.description:
The Drakes Pride Megan Blouse is super soft and has a fluid drape. 

The Sportec material from which these garments are manufactured was developed using an innovative moisture management treatment. This ensures that moisture is drawn away from the body for rapid evaporation keeping the body dry and at a balanced temperature.

Look great and feel truly comfortable on the green.

Features:
* 100% Sportec material.
* Pattern print on upper chest.
* ¼ Chrome zipper.
* Moisture wicking & anti-bacterial.
* Leisure fit.
* 150 GSM / UPF rating 'Excellent'.

fields.name: Drakes Pride Montanna Ladies Fleece
fields.description:
The Drakes Pride Montanna with its heavyweight 280gsm thermo micro fleece is a premium quality fleece. 

It is comfortable, quick drying, moisture wicking and breathable.

The fleece provides excellent insulation and can be worn as an outer layer in moderate, dry weather or as a mid-layer in colder, rainy weather under a shell layer.

This stylish, but practical fleece, comes with a high level storage pocket and two hand warmer pockets. The contrasting grey shoulder panel gives it a very appealing, modern look.

fields.name: Drakes Pride Montanna Mens Fleece
fields.description:
The Drakes Pride Montanna with its heavyweight 280gsm thermo micro fleece is a premium quality fleece. 

It is comfortable, quick drying, moisture wicking and breathable.

The fleece provides excellent insulation and can be worn as an outer layer in moderate, dry weather or as a mid-layer in colder, rainy weather under a shell layer.

This stylish but practical fleece comes with a high level storage pocket and two hand warmer pockets. The contrasting grey shoulder panel gives it a very appealing, modern look.

fields.name: Drakes Pride Robin Shirt
fields.description:
The Drakes Pride Robin Shirt is super soft and superbly comfortable, but the focal point is the design - it’s really different and very attractive. With the fluid drape it’s a shirt that will be envied.

The 100% Sportec material from which the Robin is made was developed using an innovative moisture management treatment. This ensures moisture is drawn away from the body keeping you nice and dry.

Features:
* 100% Sportec material
* Knitted collar and cuff with contrast edging
* Leisure fit
* Three button placket
* 150 GSM/UPF Rating - excellent.

NB// Drakes Pride are discontinuing the Robin shirt and size options are currently limited to S, XL & XXXL.

fields.name: Drakes Pride Rose Blouse
fields.description:
The Drakes Pride Rose Blouse with its stylish pattern and pink trim has a superb look and feel. The material is super soft to handle and has a fluid drape.

The Sportec material from which this garment is made was developed using an innovative moisture management treatment. This ensures moisture is drawn away from the body for rapid evaporation keeping the body dry.

Features:
* 100% Sportec material.
* Stylish pattern print on the front.
* Moisture wicking and anti-bacterial.
* ¼ Chrome Zip.
* Leisure fit.

fields.name: Drakes Pride Victor Bodywarmer
fields.description:
The Drakes Pride Victor Bodywarmer is both warm and comfortable whilst still leaving room for plenty of movement for delivering the bowl.

 It’s a premium quality Wind-Tec bodywarmer with quilted padding and two zipped hand warmer pockets.

Looks good whether worn as a second or third clothing layer. With its wind and shower resistant properties and its internal storm flap this truly is high performance bowlswear.

fields.name: Drakes Pride Victoria Bodywarmer
fields.description:
The Drakes Pride Victoria Bodywarmer is both warm and comfortable whilst still leaving room for plenty of movement to deliver the Bowls. 

It’s a premium quality Wind-Tec bodywarmer with quilted padding and two zipped hand warmer pockets.

Looks good whether worn as a second or third clothing layer. With its wind and shower resistant properties and its internal storm flap this truly is high performance bowlswear.

fields.name: Emsmorn Classic Shirt
fields.description:
The Emsmorn Classic Shirt fabric is a Polyester Sportec Knit that's both moisture wicking and breathable. 

It also has quick dry and anti UV properties. 

With its soft knitted collar and two button neck placket it is indeed a comfortable, classic shirt.

fields.name: Emsmorn Drilite Unisex Jacket
fields.description:
The Emsmorn Unisex Drilite Jacket is lined giving it a comfortable feel, particularly on bare arms.

It has a bright white Teflon coated lightweight polyester outer shell with 2000WP/MVT 100% waterproof and microporous breathable pigmented PU coating. There's a stitch and taped seam construction too making it even more robust and weather proof.

The Drilite Waterproof Bowls Jacket has a concealed hood in a storm collar, full length zip with internal placket, raglan sleeve, toggled drawcord hem, adjustable storm cuffs, side s

Why buy an Emsmorn Unisex Drilite Waterproof Jacket?
* Over 25 years of Emsmorn experience in making quality waterproofs for Bowlers.
* Incorporates all essential design features within a keen price.
* Waterproof & breathability on a budget.
* Machine washable but recommend hand wash for maximum lifespan.

fields.name: Emsmorn Unisex Gilet
fields.description:
The Emsmorn Unisex Gilet is bright white with a Teflon coated showerproof polyester Microfibre outer shell. There's also a fleece lining - very cosy and soft.

It's a snug fitting reversible style Bowls Bodywarmer with a full length zip. It has a padded mandarin collar, outer zip placket, vertical front pockets set into the seams, and a kidney warmer back shape. To finish, there's silver grey piping in the seams and hem.

This is a unisex item so we would politely recommend Ladies select one size down.

Why buy an Emsmorn Unisex Reversible Bowls Gilet?:
* Rustle free super soft Microfibre peached feel fabric.
* Water & stain resistant outer and warm fleece inner.
* Reversible design Stain resistant Teflon fabric.
* Machine washable at low temperature.

fields.name: Emsmorn Ventilit Jacket
fields.description:
The Emsmorn Unisex Ventilite Jacket is bright white and Teflon coated. 

It has an ultra soft feel with a 2oz polyester outer shell coated with the new 5000WP/MVT 100% waterproof and microporous breathable pigmented TPU. 

The best bit is the fabric is whisper silent - that's so nice. The seams are stitched and taped and it's all fully lined. This Waterproof Bowls Jacket is proving very popular indeed.

The jacket has stylish silver grey piping into body seams, with contrasting grey waterproof front zip and matching zips on the front pockets. There's adjustable rubber cuff tabs and a foldaway hood too.

As this is a Unisex garment we would politely recommend a size smaller for Ladies.

Why buy an Emsmorn Unisex Ventilite Jacket?
* Over 25 years of Emsmorn experience in supplying performance waterproofs for Bowls.
* Incorporates every feature Bowlers require.
* Design allows total freedom of movement in play.
* Highly waterproof /breathable shell ensures you remain both dry and comfortable.
* Bright white appearance.
* Can be machine washed but recommend hand wash for maximum lifespan.

fields.name: Emsmorn Zippy Blouse
fields.description:
The Emsmorn Zippy Blouse is a 100% polyester knit performance fabric, with 3M Scotchguard treatment. 

It's an attractive, fashionable sporty blouse with shirt collar, short set-in sleeves and a short zip at the front. It is a good fitting blouse and it's probably our most popular.

Why buy an Emsmorn Bowls Blouse?
* Cool feel performance fabric with stain resistant finish.
* Flattering set-in sleeve design.
* Worn either over or tucked in.
* Ideal warm weather garment.
* Machine washable.

fields.name: Fruit of the Loom Hooded Jacket

fields.name: Hensilite Lowland Blouse

Manufactured with exceptional quality it is stylish, breathable, anti-static, anti-UV and has moisture wicking properties. The collar with its modern ¼ zip collar lends the finishing touch.

fields.name: Hensilite Mens Jacket
fields.description: The Henselite Mens Jacket with full zip has a Polyester Soft-shell outer fabric with brushed fleece inside. The mesh under-arm panels aid breathability.

fields.name: Hensilite Victory Mens Shirt

Avaliable in White & Grey

* Excellent wear & wash characteristics, anti-pilling & UV stability.
* Regular fit matching high street sizing.
* Comfort of bi-stretch fabric especially when delivering bowling.
* Higher waistline to accommodate bending movement of delivery.
* Deep pockets for accessories.
* Machine washable.

fields.name: Emsmorn Drilite Unisex Trousers

The fabric is a jersey style knitted material with soft cotton woven into the reverse side giving extraordinary comfort.  

Taylor Mens Trousers have a full elasticated waistband, buttoned back pocket, two front facing side pockets and stitching detailing on the front crease line of the trousers to minimise ironing.

Avaliable in White and Grey.
